        <div class="row" style="margin:30px 0px">
            <article class="col-md-5">
                <div>
                    <b>原密码：（* 必填）</b>
                    <div class="form-floating mb-3">
                        <input type="email" class="form-control" id="floatingInput" placeholder="不少于4哥字符">
                    </div>
                    <b>新密码：（* 必填）</b>
                    <div class="input-group mb-3">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="不少于4哥字符" aria-label="Recipient's username" aria-describedby="basic-addon2">
                    </div>
                    <b>确认密码：（* 必填）</b>
                    <div class="input-group mb-3">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="请在输入一次密码" aria-label="Recipient's username" aria-describedby="basic-addon2">
                    </div>
                    <div style="margin-top: 10px">
                        <button class="btn btn-primary" style=" background-color: #337ab7">提交</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-light">重置</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            <aside class="col-md-6 offset-md-1">
                <div class="text-info" style="font-size:30px;margin-bottom:20px">
                    <span class="fa fa-question-circle"></span>
                    <span>说明</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <ol>
                        <li>
                            <p>即使在已登录的状态下，也要再输入一次“原密码”，是出于安全性的考虑。</p>
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </aside>
        </div>
